posts.post_title: 1912 T202 Triple Folders 20 card lot (lots of scans)
posts.post_content: Up for auction is this lot of T202 cards.  There are 20 different Triple Folders in this lot.  I have included front & back scans of all cards...note: these larger scans exaggerate any flaws but wanted to be honest on condition.  Lot is for sale for $1800 or b/o.  Please email at:  [url]cuda_1966@hotmail.com[/url].  Thanks for looking. (note, scans of last two cards can be emailed....i was only able to upload the 1st 18 cards... the final two are: "Too Late for Devlin" w/Myers & Crandall and "Wheat Strikes Out" w/Wheat & Dahlen)
Are you determined to sell it as a lot or would you break it up?

I would like to see a pic of the 1966 cuda. I'll dig up a pic of my 1973 dodge charger 440/4speed hemi orange.
